                                tags: ["post", "guide", "mira"],
                                title: "How's it going after receiving 5 $Mira......",
                                content:
                                    'As many of you may know, there has been an exciting [10,000 USDC incentive plan](https://xlog.xlog.app/creator-incentive-plan) recently announced. Fortunately, I have been tipped 5 $Mira on Crossbell. In this article, I will show you how to eventually swap it for 5 USDC on Polygon.\n\n1. To swap for USDC on Polygon, the first step is to transfer the $Mira from Crossbell to the Polygon network at the bridge: [https://mira.crossbell.io/](https://mira.crossbell.io/).\n2. Once $Mira is on Polygon, it can be swapped for USDC on [Uniswap](https://app.uniswap.org/#/swap?inputCurrency=0x27e56fc93a7c9f7ad220c1206ef03ed303bd648b):\n    - Select Polygon Network at the top right corner.\n      ![Screenshot 2023-03-21 at 01.28.49](ipfs://bafybeifsjau6ekmjykwicdhup2amraggl2qpnjplw2iahygk3n5ai5onpu)\n\n    - Connect your wallet, choose the amount of Mira you want to swap, and select USDC or any other desired token.\n    - Confirm the transaction and you\'re done!\n\n\nTo make it more clear, I also record a video: \n<video controls src="https://cloudflare-ipfs.com/ipfs/QmVcJ2z6kuMXiaco4zCpPuHk6MpA3sQoB6GkLmQndrJgfs/After receiving Mira.mp4"></video>\n\n',
